Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:41.11,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(28,649)}I sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:41.11,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}That time at the GARAGE I saw a dream about unchangeable HEART.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.11,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,So this day and the same tomorrow gets mixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.11,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}I'm roaring noisily\N around in sensibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:49.12,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,My singing heart plays the BEAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.12,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}There's definite evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.12,Trans 02.1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it in your hands.
