Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.08,Trans 02.1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.09,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,Gets revealed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:21:59.96,Trans 02.1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.46,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,Gets adjusted to the ordinary time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.22,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the way it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:09.35,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,Following the unclear yellow light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.35,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,Go through the darkest nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:13.39,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time I was too afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:13.39,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm sending off my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:17.48,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,You always reflect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:17.48,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,In my proud heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:21.57,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,We should only protect our beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.61,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,Embrace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:25.57,Trans 01,,0000,0000,0000,,It starts all over everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:25.57,Trans 02,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drowning in the raging waves.
