Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:03.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the magnetic field, for 800 years…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:07.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eibon's most powerful tool, BREW, ceased functioning and became useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It all ended up like this. We cannot be fooling around any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:18.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good news, having the major BREW falling into our hands instead of Shibusen's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:24.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,While they're defenceless, we should follow our next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it is as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:36.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going, the research on the moral manipulation machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:40.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The research is in its final stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't take much more time until it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:47.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:51.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pff, there is no need for us to rely on such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:57.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen's dummies, just let me beat the crap out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:01:01.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it seems like you didn't manage to win much in the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:06.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make sure we didn't get thrashed and have people run back with their tails between their legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:10.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My duty was different from yours since it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:18.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your words, or you'll end up receiving a beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Try me, senile immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito, continue with the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:37.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:47.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're linking up and increasing the efficiency of the construction worldwide, so everything has been going smoothly as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear, so then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:01.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, my cute children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:09.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first step in the flourishing of Arachnophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:03:43.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:48.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, the ones that attacked us were Arachnophobia's elite forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:54.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In the classroom, I am the nice and diligent student, while outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The wild animal, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, all we did was to successfully attack an old meatball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And sadly, BREW has landed into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That fact will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's... the anti-demon wavelength?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What that guy Mosquito said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That abnormal blast of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it could create such a powerful technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have any sort of relation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:50.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, all we've accomplished was just a small skirmish. We gained nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if I should go and talk to Shinigami-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:03.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's kinda depressed, uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:10.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... In the end, BREW was taken away by Arachnophobia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And why would that be so depressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you think about it for a while, just by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, by the way, what's up with Kid-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:27.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going to the toilet but he hasn't returned yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that guy run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:40.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A Great Detective's First Case
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:40.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen's Secret Exposed by Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen is... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What is my honorable father planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:06:02.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon tools that Eibon created; sending the Shibusen's troops out to battle without revealing his true intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:08.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He simply said it was to prevent it from falling into evil hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But throughout all this time, I don't think that's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is Eibon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of relationship does he have with my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked him for a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,honorable father just gave a lame answer or changed the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that seems to be the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall investigate right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaah!~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:58.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, as I was saying, Kid has held some suspicions towards you lately, Shinigami-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have started his own solo investigation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. This is confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it confidential!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's quite disturbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be good if you just throw it into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:32.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell it honestly, I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:38.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuously collecting the demon tools from Eibon. What on earth are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just ask you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not going to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello hello, Shinigami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:07.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shinigami-sama... There's something I want to ask you... Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you a-ny-thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's the difference here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A anti-demon's wavelength?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Mosquito said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:28.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,When i intended to use Witch Hunter, and he said, the anti-demon... does it have some sort of relation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:33.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Maka's became able to perform the Demon Hunter technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's not that great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:41.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Maka-chan for you; you really resemble your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:50.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About the anti-demon resonance... It's a unique ability that your mother has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My... Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:59.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like its name, it's a kind of special resonance that can vanquish evil forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:06.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka-chan's mother has this ability, and she was superior to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:12.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But, who would have thought? You managed to perform the Demon Hunter technique! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:18.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Going at this speed, maybe you could even defeat the Kishin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:25.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was alive, I was, as well, a man who could flatter very well. That was the kind of man I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:32.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, there's still more hardships to come.\NYou have to keep working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability that my mother has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that Maka's abilities would awaken this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:57.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe the power to annihilate the Kishin really is in her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, now, now, Sid-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:00.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing... Have you settled it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:11.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I ask you to bring the guy from Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, about that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It will be settled real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through a lot of danger and into the magnetic field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And at that moment, there was an enormous explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole scene was a huge spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. What is there for you to be proud of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:32.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:42.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing, wasn't it? The battle at Lost Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggles happened all around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And that guy can still brag around and be proud of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:56.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, BREW was taken by Arachnophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:04.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But that... Soul's piano playing was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If we didn't have him, I don't know in what sort of situation we would be in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:15.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone returned safe and sound. And I think that's the most important thing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:17.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe and sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Professor Stein is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor S-Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At the island, he suddenly collapsed. It was disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he's resting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be glad if it was nothing but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't done those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Stein...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Crona?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, no... It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd fella...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Crona, Hurry up and finish your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:10.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where do you plan to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where "there" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we forget about it, we have to quickly grasp the feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that the power could possible topple the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're having this special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not there... It's not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said it's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That... that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Stein... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:11.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine? Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:17.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I say that, no one probably thinks that I'm alright, true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is this thing named "BREW"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:36.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing known as BREW is one of the demon tools,\Nand even in the numerous demon tools, it is Eibon's greatest creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:41.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like his name, it is a tool that contains demonic magic abilities within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:46.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And according to the wielder, the effects of using it can be vastly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:50.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you just another shallow question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What does my father plan to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What of the effects after using that demon tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know, just speculate. That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hear Professor's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So what will you do after you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:18.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you have been waiting for this, but whatever I tell you will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:23.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, will you fully accept what I say when I'm actually on this state?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:24.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:33.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to say that you are willing to listen. But after you hear it, what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, special training is not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of thing should be done by main characters in shonen manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:45.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. Here, hurry and transform into a scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:46.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Resonance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:19.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it the Witch Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it not become the Demon Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you are being lazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:44.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding. If I was lazing around, how would the Witch Hunter be performed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Explaining this is no simple task...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the troubled face, Maka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why we are having this special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.27,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Arachne has...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she has sent out spiders throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:28.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like she's starting to move ahead. She must be up to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:33.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for troubling you. If there's any news, keep me informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is moving along...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And then? Any changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing out of the ordinary....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you know where they keep the demon tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That too, not quite yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to remain in Shibusen, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:07.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About that matter... of Marie-sensei's snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that... Professor Stein... He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I forgot to mention that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to that snake, BREW has fallen into our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Without even a battle, two people cannot fight already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is... the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,N-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:41.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, continue with your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa is anticipating you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:02.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How tough... it's alright for us to stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, get up. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, we could indeed use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we did it. Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:29.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it came out once already, it will surely come out again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huhhh, I'm hungry. Today is Maka's turn to cook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to do the shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight will be cup noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You must clear your suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I can see something and pretend I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is true... Even for your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course no one will be excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone that deviates from the right path must be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, who lays out the right path?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And how would you know if they have deviated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:21.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who they are, they would be able to recognize the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:33.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I ask you this: About this truth, who on earth bestowed it upon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:38.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start, the world relies on the reason created by the filthy adults to keep rotating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:43.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth always contains the thoughts and principles of the authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:48.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,From where should we start to talk about the actual original condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:55.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, the truth that you speak of has long ago been wrecked to a mere skeleton of a concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of trash like thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it just happens so it fits the truth of what you are seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.43,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still no different from a puzzle one cannot control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so determined on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that you wouldn't keep on asking those kinds of blaming questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't even some sort of third rate instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:31.96,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, isn't Shibusen the people who are last?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:44.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, I completely disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:49.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen is no shallow organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he has arrived;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:11.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,the consultant of the European technology development division, Buttadaki Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,From today onwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work around here.
